    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/43749a3e0fee7a716c0a63bdaf7baa89.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/43749a3e0fee7a716c0a63bdaf7baa89.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/43749a3e0fee7a716c0a63bdaf7baa89.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CASE 是一款最多 8 人参与的回合制策略游戏。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的主要目标是与另一位玩家结盟，消灭地图上的所有敌人。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你选择一个区域开始游戏，并在和平阶段完成你的基地建设。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在区域上放置镐和盾牌以进行生产和防御，并可升级至 3 级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/14634b0bdf3d9ebd2dbbe51dad5be8b4.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/14634b0bdf3d9ebd2dbbe51dad5be8b4.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/14634b0bdf3d9ebd2dbbe51dad5be8b4.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你扩展版图，你有机会找到各种独特卡牌；如何战略性地使用这些卡牌完全取决于你。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发展卡帮助你更快成长。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/58218afd87602a74e547e603d0b60327.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/58218afd87602a74e547e603d0b60327.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/58218afd87602a74e547e603d0b60327.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击卡让你与敌人战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/5d61f7e653b0461695272fe0d20d7dbb.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/5d61f7e653b0461695272fe0d20d7dbb.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/5d61f7e653b0461695272fe0d20d7dbb.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陷阱卡让试图征服你的敌人措手不及。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/edaed920a43cb786343f7b9edbc3b8cf.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/edaed920a43cb786343f7b9edbc3b8cf.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/edaed920a43cb786343f7b9edbc3b8cf.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >政治卡让你干预其他玩家的策略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/69c201f3ab71902448ab66e6dd097783.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/69c201f3ab71902448ab66e6dd097783.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/69c201f3ab71902448ab66e6dd097783.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记住，在 CASE 中，只要最终获胜，一切都是值得的。加入战场，与敌人作战吧！</p></li></ul>",
